OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,FA newly qualified social worker is
OL,7,Fhelping vulnerable children thanks to
OL,8,Fher inspirational father-in-law, who
OL,9,Ftaught thousands about the profession
OL,10,Fbefore he died at the age of 55.
OL,12,FWhen Alice Powney-Dugdale met Dr Daryl
OL,13,FDugdale he was already living with
OL,14,Fterminal lung cancer.
OL,16,FIn the 18 months she knew him, Dr
OL,17,FDugdale made a lasting impression ` as
OL,18,Fhe had done with so many others.
