OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,FOften described as "larger than life"
OL,7,Fand "unconventional", he was a music
OL,8,Ffanatic, a DJ and a regular at Bristol
OL,9,FCity matches.
OL,11,FHis lifelong pursuit of social justice
OL,12,Fled him to a career in social work and
OL,13,Feventually to programme director of
OL,14,Fthe University of Bristol's MSc in
OL,15,Fsocial work, where he helped train the
OL,16,Fnext generation of social workers.
OL,18,FHe died in May 2021 and a month later,
OL,19,FAlice was accepted onto the course he
OL,20,Fused to run.
