OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,FDr Dugdale's widow, Tracey Close, was
OL,7,Fa student on the same social work
OL,8,Fcourse in the 1990s and Alice's
OL,9,Fhusband, Zak Powney-Dugdale, is a
OL,10,Fyouth worker.
OL,12,FDuring the course, Alice, who grew up
OL,13,Fin Radstock, Somerset and now lives in
OL,14,FBristol, learnt she was dyslexic and
OL,15,Fmay have ADHD.
OL,17,FThe 26-year-old said: "The only reason
OL,18,FI managed to finish my dissertation is
OL,19,Fbecause I wanted to dedicate it to
OL,20,FDaryl. The dedication is now framed in
OL,21,Fmy office.
OL,26,@yD@WOU
