OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,F"As the course went on he gave me a
OL,7,Fweird ray of confidence, at times it
OL,8,Ffelt like he was there."
OL,10,FAlice is now working as a child
OL,11,Fprotection social worker at Bristol
OL,12,FCity Council, where she "champions"
OL,13,Fyoung people and tries to be "a person
OL,14,Fthey can depend on".
OL,16,FShe and her husband married in August
OL,17,F2023.
