OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,F"Being dyslexic, I was never supposed
OL,7,Fto do a master's and I was never
OL,8,Fsupposed to be here, so I'm so proud.
OL,9,FPassing means so much to me," she said.
OL,11,FMs Close added: "I am so proud of
OL,12,FAlice and what she has achieved. Both
OL,13,FDaryl and I were chuffed when we knew
OL,14,FZak was going out with someone who
OL,15,Fwanted to make a difference in our
OL,16,Fworld and was considering becoming a
OL,17,Fsocial worker.
