OL,3,CLate academic praised after daughter-
OL,4,Cin-law becomes social worker
OL,6,F"Both Daryl and I qualified as social
OL,7,Fworkers from Bristol in the 1990s and
OL,8,FDaryl really thought he had won the
OL,9,Flottery when he became a teaching
OL,10,Ffellow on the course that had inspired
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,F"Daryl was so happy that Alice had
OL,14,Fapplied for the course and her journey
OL,15,Fthrough the course and working in the
OL,16,Fsame office that he started as a
OL,17,Fsocial worker feels like he is beside
OL,18,Fus and guiding her."
